message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with speech processing and analysis. cs.CL is also likely as it deals with natural language processing and speech is a form of natural language. cs.LG is another possible category as it deals with machine learning techniques, which are used in the proposed framework. cs.CV is also possible as it deals with computer vision and image processing, which are related to spectrogram analysis. cs.SI is less likely but still possible as it deals with signal processing, which is relevant to speech separation.
